<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039189" n="1"/> 
<opener><salute>Viro Clarissimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-117260266" type="person">Jacobo Stirling</rs></salute> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person">N. B.</rs></opener>
  <p>Quamvis ad ultimas meas <rs type="letter">litteras</rs> ante quinque<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>ium ad Te datas
    <lb/>nullum responsum tulerim, non tamen credo eas Tibi omni ex
    <lb/>parte displicuisse, aut animum Tuum ob qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dam libere sed
    <lb/>amice dicta abs me abalienatum esse. Hinc est quod non du<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>bitaverim <rs type="person">latorem</rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentium Tibi co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endare. Is est Vir
    <lb/>Juvenis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissimus <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-100289665" type="person">Jallabertus Genevensis</rs>, olim Pro<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>fessoris Matheseos non incelebris <rs type="person">filius</rs>, et <rs key="pers_DE-588-11670912X" type="person">Crameri</rs> nostri disci<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>pulus, qui aliquandiu apud nos moratus<del><gap/></del> nunc iter suum litte<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>rarium in <rs key="place_VER-belgie" type="place">Belgium</rs> <add>et <rs key="place_VER-englan" type="place">Angliam</rs></add> prosequitur, ubi ex doctissimorum Viro<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>rum, Tuo pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim, alloquio et co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ercio proficere cupiens
    <lb/>hasce ad Te co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatitias <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me petiit. Rogo itaque, ut co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>oda
    <lb/>ipsius adjuvare <del><gap/></del>velis, Tibique persuadeas, quicquid grati
    <lb/>ipsi feceris, hoc mihi ipsi et <rs type="person">Cramero</rs> nostro gratissimum
    <lb/>fore. Doleo me per alia studia atque negotia <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> rebus Mathe<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>maticis avocatum nihil novi Tibi impertiri posse. Ne tamen
    <lb/>omnino sit sterilis h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c mea epistola, hoc unicum ex aliena quidem penu<!-- ToDo: kontrollieren --> depromtum, Tibi forte non ingratum, Tecum
    <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicandum esse duxi. Narratum mihi est, <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Eulerum</rs> no<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>stratem <rs key="place_GEO-498817" type="place">Petroburgi</rs> Matheseos sublimioris Professorem singula<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>re quid circa seriem reciprocam quadratorum <choice><orig><formula>1 + \frac{1}{4} + \frac{1}{9} + \frac{1}{16} + \mathrm{\;\&amp;c.}</formula></orig><reg><formula>1 + \frac{1}{4} + \frac{1}{9} + \frac{1}{16} + \mathrm{\;etc.}</formula></reg></choice>
    <lb/>detexisse, nempe sextuplum ejus su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quari quadrato circum<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ferenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> circuli, cujus diameter est unitas, quod optime convenit
    <lb/>cum numero 1.6449340668 <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr> quem Tu per tuas elegantissi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
    <pb facs="1039190" n="2"/> 
    <lb break="no"/>mas methodos invenisti. Deduxit hoc inventum <rs key="pers_DE-588-118531379" type="person">Eulerus</rs> per metho<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>dum indirectam ex <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quatione infinita <choice><orig><formula>y=x-\frac{x^{3}}{6}+\frac{x^{5}}{120}-\frac{x^{7}}{5040}+\mathrm{\&amp;c.}</formula></orig><reg><formula>y=x-\frac{x^{3}}{6}+\frac{x^{5}}{120}-\frac{x^{7}}{5040}+\mathrm{etc.}</formula></reg></choice>
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, ut notum est, exprimit relationem inter sinum <formula>y</formula> et arcum <formula>x</formula>
    <lb/>pro radio circuli <formula>= 1</formula>. Nempe posito sinu <formula>y=0</formula>, designabunt radices
    <lb/>hujus <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quationis <choice><orig><formula>0=x-\frac{x^{3}}{6}+\frac{x^{5}}{120}-\mathrm{\&amp;c.}</formula></orig><reg><formula>0=x-\frac{x^{3}}{6}+\frac{x^{5}}{120}-\mathrm{etc.}</formula></reg></choice> omnes valores arcuum quorum
    <lb/>sinus sunt <formula>=0</formula>, id est, posita <formula>C=</formula> circumferenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> circuli cujus diameter
    <lb/>est unitas, vel <add>=</add> semicircumferenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> circuli cujus radius <formula>= 1</formula>, radices hujus
    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quationis infinit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> erunt <formula>0</formula>, <formula>C</formula>, <formula>2C</formula>, <formula>3C</formula>, <formula>4C</formula>, <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr> sive dividendo per <formula>x</formula>
    <lb/>radices hujus <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quationis <choice><orig><formula>0=1-\frac{xx}{6}+\frac{x^{4}}{120}-\mathrm{\&amp;c.}</formula></orig><reg><formula>0=1-\frac{xx}{6}+\frac{x^{4}}{120}-\mathrm{etc.}</formula></reg></choice> erunt <formula>C</formula>, <formula>2C</formula>, <formula>3C</formula>, <formula>4C</formula>, <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr> vel
    <lb/>posito <formula>xx=\frac{1}{z}</formula>, radices hujus <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quationis <choice><orig><formula>0=1-\frac{1}{6z}+\frac{1}{120z^{2}}-\mathrm{\;\&amp;c.}</formula></orig><reg><formula>0=1-\frac{1}{6z}+\frac{1}{120z^{2}}-\mathrm{\;etc.}</formula></reg></choice> erunt <formula>\frac{1}{C^{2}}</formula>, <formula>\frac{1}{4C^{2}}</formula>,
    <lb/><formula>\frac{1}{9C^{2}}</formula>, <formula>\frac{1}{16C^{2}}</formula>, <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr> Hinc quia in omni <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quatione algebraica, ubi termini se<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>cundum dignitates descendentes indeterminat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> disponuntur, coefficiens
    <lb/>secundi termini sub signo negativo exprimit su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>am omnium radicum,
    <lb/>erit hic <choice><orig><formula>\frac{1}{6}=\frac{1}{C^{2}}\times\frac{1}{1}+\frac{1}{4}+\frac{1}{9}+\frac{1}{16}+\mathrm{\&amp;c.}</formula></orig><reg><formula>\frac{1}{6}=\frac{1}{C^{2}}\left(\frac{1}{1}+\frac{1}{4}+\frac{1}{9}+\frac{1}{16}+\mathrm{etc.}\right)</formula></reg></choice> adeoque ipsa series <choice><orig><formula>\frac{1}{1}+\frac{1}{4}+\frac{1}{9}+\frac{1}{16}+ \mathrm{\&amp;c.}</formula></orig><reg><formula>\frac{1}{1}+\frac{1}{4}+\frac{1}{9}+\frac{1}{16}+ \mathrm{etc.}</formula></reg></choice>
    <lb/><formula>=\frac{C^{2}}{6}</formula>. <abbr>Q. E. D.</abbr> Observavi posse, sed non sine difficultate, ad eandem<del><gap/></del>
    <lb/><del><gap/></del>conclusionem perveniri methodo directa <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> priori, unde scire aveo,
    <lb/>an Tibi suppetat methodus id facilius efficiendi.</p>
  <closer>Vale et mihi fave.
    <lb/><dateline><abbr>Dab.</abbr> <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1738-04-07">7. Aprilis 1738.</date></dateline></closer>
  <pb facs="1039191" n="3" type="empty"/>
</div>
